local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["raconteur"]={"raconteur","[,rækɒn'tɜː]","[,rækɑn'tɝ]","n.善于讲故事的人",'n.善于讲故事的人','His grandfather was a fine raconteur, dredging up quite effortlessly, and with a great wealth of detail, scenes and incidents from his early life.','他的祖父是位很好讲故事的人，不废吹灰之力就把他年轻时事情、场景极详细地描绘出来。','I encountered a raconteur during my flight to Mahattan.','在飞往曼哈顿的旅途，我碰到了一位很好讲故事的人。'}
